# Frontend preservation (BIHE)

**Do not redesign or modify the frontend UI/UX.**

## Must preserve (identical appearance)

- Existing HTML structure
- Existing CSS classes
- Existing responsiveness
- Existing animations
- Existing layout hierarchy
- Existing JavaScript functionality

## Allowed changes only

- Convert static HTML → Laravel Blade templates (`@extends`, `@section`, `@include`, `@forelse`, `{{ }}`, `@csrf`, `@error`)
- Inject dynamic database / API content
- Add backend logic, auth, admin CRUD, API routes

## Forbidden without explicit approval

- Changing colours, fonts, spacing, or breakpoints
- Renaming or removing CSS classes
- Replacing vanilla JS with frameworks or build pipelines on Hostinger
- Redesigning components, layouts, or navigation chrome
- Adding new visual UI patterns not present in the source HTML

## Project layout

| Surface | Frontend source | Dynamic layer |
|---------|-----------------|---------------|
| Public website | Next.js + existing CSS (`src/`, `src/styles/`) | Fetch from Laravel `/api/v1/*` later — **do not change public UI when wiring data** |

## Homepage sections (public site)

**Dynamic only** (via `src/lib/api/homepage.ts`):

- Hero banners
- Announcements / notices
- News & events
- Gallery highlights
- Recruiters / partners logos

**Keep static** (hardcoded in components or `src/lib/*-content.ts`):

- About content
- Principal message
- Statistics
- Academic / courses information
- Accreditation, facilities, and all other informational sections

## Phase 1 static pages (no CMS / API)

**Do not wire these to Laravel admin or `/api/v1/*` in Phase 1.** Content stays in `src/lib/*-content.ts` and page components. Canonical list: `src/lib/phase1-static-pages.ts`.

| Category | Routes (examples) |
|----------|-------------------|
| About Us | `/about-bihe`, `/recognition`, `/annual-reports`, … |
| Vision & Mission | `/institutional-development-plan` (`idp-content.ts`) |
| IQAC | `/academics/iqac` |
| NAAC | Homepage `#accreditation` + IQAC copy (no dedicated NAAC page yet) |
| Principal Message | `/principal`, homepage `PrincipalMessage.tsx` |
| Academic Calendar | `/academics/academic-calendar` |
| Committee pages | `/governing-bodies`, `/internal-complaint-committee`, `/ombudsperson`, … |
| Admission information | `/admissions/*`, international students admission |
| Academic information | `/academics/bca`, `/academics/b-com`, library, examination, … |

**Already dynamic in Phase 1** (outside the list above): homepage hero/announcements/news/gallery/recruiters, `/news/*`, `/gallery/*`, faculty roster on `/academics/faculty-and-staff`, contact form.

| Admin panel | `bihe-admin/public/assets/` + `resources/views/` | Laravel controllers, models, Blade loops |

When in doubt: copy HTML verbatim into Blade, then add directives only where data varies.
